{
  "texts": [
    "Common audio datasets used in speech research include LJ Speech, JSUT, and RUSLAN.",
    "Many studies (Yuan et al., 2024) (Huang et al., 2023) (Ghosh et al., 2024) in the field also rely on audio data as a primary source.",
    "Common video datasets used in research include HMDB, UCF101, and ASLAN.",
    "Many studies (Chen et al., 2023) (He et al., 2023) (Yin et al., 2019) in the field of RALM utilize audio data as a source of information.",
    "This section provides a summary of the downstream tasks that the RALM architecture primarily focuses on."
  ]
}